name: SeaSynth - Synthesizer Instrument UI + Kits
description:
Hey guys!

Today, Inspired by "ROLI seaboard" and "Vital," I created a software synthesizer UI Concept and kit.

This project took a long time to create, so please consider making a donation through Buy Me a Coffee.


Includes:

  • Full UI Concept Design
  • Interactive Seaboard (Keyboard) Component
  • Knobs, Slides
  • Other Kits


Tell me about your suggestions, and I'll incorporate them as soon as possible. ❤️
